  <summary date="2023-08-08T23:16:16Z" status="Introduced in House">Displaced Afghan Women and Girls Education Act of 2022

This bill provides certain educational resources to certain displaced Afghan women and girls domiciled in the United States. 

For example, the bill (1) requires such displaced Afghan women and girls to receive in-state tuition rates at public institutions of higher education, and (2) provides funding for and establishes the Displaced Afghan Women and Girls Scholarship Grant.</summary>
